<body>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> February 6, 2026</p>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>
    <p>TheHabitMethod ("we", "our", or "us") operates an automated content publishing system for Pinterest. This policy
        explains how we handle data.</p>

    <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
    <p>Our Pinterest automation tool collects only the data necessary to post content to Pinterest on your behalf:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Pinterest account authentication tokens</li>
        <li>Board names and IDs</li>
        <li>Pin performance analytics (saves, impressions)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Data</h2>
    <p>We use this data solely to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Post pins to your Pinterest boards</li>
        <li>Analyze pin performance to improve content</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>All data is stored locally on your machine. We do not transmit your data to external servers.</p>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the Pinterest API to post content. Pinterest's own privacy policy applies to your Pinterest account.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>For questions about this policy, contact us through our website.</p>
